TABLE OF CONTENTS
------------------

A.  SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
B.  INSTALLATION
C.  SUPPORT


A. SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS
-----------------------
   
  - Microsoft Windows (>)10 or Linux
  - python 3 (>3.8 suggested) with tkinter
  - g++ <= 11 (linux)
   

B. INSTALLATION
----------------

Windows:
	- run bin/JanusPy.pyw for GUI mode or bin/JanusC.exe for console mode

Linux:
	- cd in Janus directory
	- run sudo sh Janus_Install.sh and check if any required package is missing
	- run bin/JanusPy.pyw for GUI mode or bin/JanusC for console mode

C. SUPPORT   
-----------
        
For technical support, go to https://www.caen.it/mycaen/support/ (login and MyCAEN+ account required)
